sections.heading: to 61-28A-28 - Repealed.
sections.text: Repeals.— Laws 1999, ch. 179, § 31 repealed 61-28A-1 to 61-28A-28 NMSA 1978, as enacted by Laws 1992, ch. 10, §§ 1, 2, 4 to 7, 10 to 12, 14, 16, 20 to 23, 25, 26 and 28 and Laws 1993, ch. 83, § 6, and as amended by Laws 1993, ch. 340, §§ 1 to 3 and 5 to 8 and Laws 1997, ch. 207, §§ 1 and 2, relating to public accountancy, effective July 1, 1999. For provisions of former sections,seethe 1998 NMSA 1978 onNMOneSource.com. For present comparable provisions,see61-28B-1 NMSA et seq.
